{"tid":962731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國傳促中方 公布貿易建議細節","createTime":"2018-12-31T05:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T10:35:33.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"196a05cf3341adf0ebe71e92ead83e3dd93dc05a","tid":962731,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"美國傳促中方 公布貿易建議細節<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/china/article/2026804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F2026804&d=Vzlor4zzsfsTuJsoLHP5MS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=6920046e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/china/article/2026804</a><br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》引述消息人士稱，美國正迫使中國在貿易與投資建議上提出更多具體細節，以化解彼此之間的分歧。<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平與美國總統特朗普在12月1日於阿根廷舉行雙邊會談後，同意貿易戰「停火」90天。特朗普當時指出，北京政府同意作出購買更多美國貨與停止向部分美國產品徵收關稅，以及開放本土市場的做法。不過，中國一直沒有進一步公布細節。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指出，美國政府官員多次敦促北京政府，公布更多開放市場細節以落實承諾。<br />\n<br />\n上周六，特朗普披露當天與習近平通電話，事情取得重大進展。不過，《華爾街日報》引述消息人士稱，特朗普可能誇大了雙方談判進展。"},{"pid":"9efb6bd6b346c2c3cb65d471ef0d871a80d17ad6","tid":962731,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:55:55.000Z","msg":"怕你反口唔認數"},{"pid":"0c6c9aba9e23acd0fa748349eb5746eb5dae3c47","tid":962731,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:19:13.000Z","msg":"講嚟講去都係中國降番低關稅買多啲美國貨開放中國市場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb9b3a67d399e5eb7f62dad6118575f145a2f24","tid":962731,"uid":44358,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0c6c9aba9e23acd0fa748349eb5746eb5dae3c47","tid":962731,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:19:13.000Z","msg":"講嚟講去都係中國降番低關稅買多啲美國貨開放中國市場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:27:50.000Z","msg":"重點係開放市場，保護外國知識產權同埋唔准再玩商業間諜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47f099ec706e2e90e9bffaccdce2170cbc10397","tid":962731,"uid":192190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:29:21.000Z","msg":"侵侵呢排同民主黨玩到慶烚烚, 同習種呢邊吹大D好正常<br />\n遲D同民主黨講掂數再撚鳩習種<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32dde6a39e20625aa19801c623beaf945ab1d9dc","tid":962731,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eb9b3a67d399e5eb7f62dad6118575f145a2f24","tid":962731,"uid":44358,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0c6c9aba9e23acd0fa748349eb5746eb5dae3c47","tid":962731,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:19:13.000Z","msg":"講嚟講去都係中國降番低關稅買多啲美國貨開放中國市場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:27:50.000Z","msg":"重點係開放市場，保護外國知識產權同埋唔准再玩商業間諜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:31:10.000Z","msg":"知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我嘅意思係全部談判結果中國一啲著數都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ab237a88191630beb9a79b8ef7dba5403b650e","tid":962731,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:33:46.000Z","msg":"等件事丟淡咪算囉<br />\n全世界都預左會不了了之架啦"},{"pid":"538b8cfeaf1f4096106c5f194d3fba3f369ad568","tid":962731,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:35:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好上水啦！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實大家都知你一早冇褲著好耐啦！！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"facbc10e8b999a0abae2c7386c80ead14b4654da","tid":962731,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:55:43.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》引述知情人士說，特朗普誇大中美雙方談判進展，他的目的是藉此安撫市場。<br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平與美國總統特朗普在周六（29日）通電話，惟雙方都沒有透露具體細節。<br />\n這通電話發生在美國聯邦政府局部停擺，以及美國股市先失卻「聖誕節反彈行情」（Santa Rally）的傳統，再發生「血色平安夜」之後。<br />\n《華爾街日報》引述知情人士說，特朗普誇大中美雙方談判進展，他的目的是藉此安撫市場。"},{"pid":"8a7ab14443287b66add630f8b10d4c8017c45533","tid":962731,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}